# 4. 母子

Mafuyu: Thanks for breakfast. I should start heading over to school.
Mafuyu's Mother: Okay, be safe. And good luck at school, Mafuyu.
Mafuyu: (Mom and I ended up talking a lot yesterday.)
Mafuyu: (Which made my chest feel so warm.)
???: <Mafuyu.>
Mafuyu: Miku, Len...
Miku: <We came to see how you were doing.>
Len: <How are you feeling, Mafuyu? Good...?>
Mafuyu: Yes...
Mafuyu: At least, I think I'm fine.
Teacher: Here you are, Asahina. I thought your essay this time around was very good.
Mafuyu: Thank you very much. I'm glad to hear it, since I did try my best on this one.
Teacher: Would it be alright if I posted this up for everyone to have a look at?
Mafuyu: Yes, if mine will suffice.
Mafuyu: I'm back, Mom.
Mafuyu's Mother: Oh, welcome home. Dinner will be ready in just a moment.
Mafuyu: Okay.
Mafuyu: Take a look at this...
Mafuyu's Mother: Huh? Oh, you got a 98? That's wonderful!
Mafuyu's Mother: Well done, Mafuyu. That's your hard work paying off. Congratulations.
Mafuyu: Thank you.
Mafuyu's Mother: Is this the song you and your friends are working on at the moment?
Mafuyu: *Nod*
Mafuyu's Mother: You're the lyricist for your group, yes? Can you tell me how you came up with the words for this one?
Mafuyu: How...?
Mafuyu: I don't know. I just write down what I feel.
Mafuyu's Mother: I see...
Mafuyu's Mother: Then, these are the things you've been feeling.
Mafuyu's Mother: Would it be alright if I listened to some of your other songs?
Mafuyu: Sure...
Emu: Hi, Asahina! I have a question about that class rep meeting!
Mafuyu: Oh, Otori, hello.
Mafuyu: Is this about that survey? I was actually hoping to discuss that with you a little further.
Emu: Oh...
Emu: Hehe. Then, let's talk about it right now!
Len: <Mafuyu seems to be feeling a lot better now...>
Miku: <Yes.>
Miku: <I'm glad...>
Mafuyu: Good morning, Mom.
Mafuyu's Mother: Good morning. Oh, I thought you didn't have school today?
Mafuyu's Mother: I was actually hoping to invite you to that Vermeer exhibit.
Mafuyu: Oh...
Mafuyu: I'm sorry. We still have club activities today...
Mafuyu's Mother: Club activities?
Mafuyu's Mother: Oh... I didn't realize you were still doing that.
Mafuyu: Huh...?
Mafuyu's Mother: Oh... I-I'm sorry. I didn't mean it like that.
Mafuyu: I'd like to continue until I have to leave to focus on preparing for my entrance exams...
Mafuyu: Would that be alright?
Mafuyu's Mother: Yes, of course. There's no problem with that at all!
Mafuyu's Mother: I know. Since you have club today, I'll go get some towels and such ready for you.
Mafuyu: No, I can do that...
Mafuyu's Mother: Nonsense. You stay put. I'll be right back with everything.
